<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=58&amp;p=7485#p7485"><![CDATA[
<div class="quotetitle">hap wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent"><br />Does the VRC7 have a different internal instrument ROM, or does it just sound different because the sound's going through the Famicom DAC before reaching our ears ? If it's using different instruments, which configuration is the most accurate one ?<br /></div><br /><br />It would appear that it does use a different instrument set than a standard YM2413 (that, or all of the people who have made YM2413 instrument sets in the past have been tone-deaf) - you can get a 99% accurate instrument set (made by Kevin Horton) from either the Nintendulator mappers or FCE Ultra.<br /><br />For convenience, the instrument set can be found below - it is up to you to determine how to transplant these instruments into your own code:<br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">static const unsigned char default_inst&#91;15&#93;&#91;8&#93; = &#123;<br />   &#123;0x03,0x21,0x04,0x06,0x8D,0xF2,0x42,0x17&#125;,<br />   &#123;0x13,0x41,0x05,0x0E,0x99,0x96,0x63,0x12&#125;,<br />   &#123;0x31,0x11,0x10,0x0A,0xF0,0x9C,0x32,0x02&#125;,<br />   &#123;0x21,0x61,0x1D,0x07,0x9F,0x64,0x20,0x27&#125;,<br />   &#123;0x22,0x21,0x1E,0x06,0xF0,0x76,0x08,0x28&#125;,<br />   &#123;0x02,0x01,0x06,0x00,0xF0,0xF2,0x03,0x95&#125;,<br />   &#123;0x21,0x61,0x1C,0x07,0x82,0x81,0x16,0x07&#125;,<br />   &#123;0x23,0x21,0x1A,0x17,0xEF,0x82,0x25,0x15&#125;,<br />   &#123;0x25,0x11,0x1F,0x00,0x86,0x41,0x20,0x11&#125;,<br />   &#123;0x85,0x01,0x1F,0x0F,0xE4,0xA2,0x11,0x12&#125;,<br />   &#123;0x07,0xC1,0x2B,0x45,0xB4,0xF1,0x24,0xF4&#125;,<br />   &#123;0x61,0x23,0x11,0x06,0x96,0x96,0x13,0x16&#125;,<br />   &#123;0x01,0x02,0xD3,0x05,0x82,0xA2,0x31,0x51&#125;,<br />   &#123;0x61,0x22,0x0D,0x02,0xC3,0x7F,0x24,0x05&#125;,<br />   &#123;0x21,0x62,0x0E,0x00,0xA1,0xA0,0x44,0x17&#125;<br />&#125;;</div><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=7">Quietust</a> — Fri Dec