<title type="html"><![CDATA[OPL2 / VRC7 / FM synth questions]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=58&amp;p=371#p371"><![CDATA[
OPL2 is YM3812.<br />OPL3 is YMF-262.<br />VRC7 is <strong>NOT</strong> an OPL2, but an OPLL, or YM2413.<br />All of these are quite different.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=7">Quietust</a> — Mon Nov 29, 2004 2:10 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
